Text: How do I get the serial to work??
thanks for no info on the program or how to install.
thanks for the torrent, one question thou.. how do you get the serials to work ?

okay, so in order to get the serial, you have to download iSerial Reader, once you got the program, open the Serial Box 09-2009.sb2 file. The iSerial Reader will ask if you want to install the file, click yes, then it will show a whole bunch of serials for all types of Mac program. Type Sketchbook Pro in search bar, and you will find the serial.
